'''Peter Imre''' is one of the richest businessmen in [[Romania]] and is also a [[food critic|restaurant critic]].Born in Zalau Salaj ,he frequently writes in ''[[Ziarul Financiar]]'' (The Financial Newspaper), and is currently the Director of Corporate Affairs for [[Philip Morris International|Philip Morris]] in Romania. He is married to Marina Meleşcanu.<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.ziua.ro/mail.php?id=39904&data=2000-03-08|title=Philip Morris Romania a lansat programul educational|publisher=Ziua|issue=1740|date=8 March 2000}}</ref>

